Repository containing the BPM firmware

===============================================

The project is based on tools developed by CERN and others:

hdl-make:
	http://www.ohwr.org/projects/hdl-make
wishbone-gen:
	http://www.ohwr.org/projects/wishbone-gen/repository
platform-independent core-collection: 
	http://www.ohwr.org/projects/general-cores/repository

===============================================

As this repository makes use of git submodules (cores folder),
use the following command to clone it.

git clone --recursive git://github.com/lerwys/BPM_project.git
or
git clione --recursive git@github.com:lerwys/BPM_project.git
